My #1 fave from the album, even though it's hella repetitive.

Are you fucking kidding? I don't even like Eminem but his part elevates the song even higher than it was already. So creepy, it's not about bullshit he's spitting (even though it's more than appropriate for a song about being on drugs), it's about his delivery, suddenly pouncing on you and going from mushy to bonkers in a matter of seconds, like he's really being higher than the sky. This song is so good I don't know where to start with.
